<i>Over 68 million Americans</i>

00:02.384 --> 00:04.418
<i>leave the safety of
our borders every year.</i>

00:04.452 --> 00:06.288
<i>If danger strikes,</i>

00:06.320 --> 00:08.389
<i>the FBI's International
Response Team</i>

00:08.422 --> 00:10.925
<i>is called into action.</i>

